description: This file is a minified JavaScript source for Bootstrap version 3.3.5, providing UI components such as alerts, buttons, carousels, modals, tooltips, popovers, scrollspy, tabs, and affix functionalities. It includes version checks for jQuery, transition support, and defines implementations for Bootstrap's interactive components.

methods.name: a.fn.emulateTransitionEnd
methods.description: Simulates the end of a transition after a specified duration.

methods.name: a.fn.alert
methods.description: Provides alert component functionality with close capability.

methods.name: a.fn.button
methods.description: Enables button state toggling and loading indication.

methods.name: a.fn.carousel
methods.description: Implements carousel/slideshow behavior for elements with sliding content.

methods.name: a.fn.dropdown
methods.description: Enables dropdown menu toggling and keyboard navigation.

methods.name: a.fn.modal
methods.description: Implements modal dialog display, hide, and management.

methods.name: a.fn.tooltip
methods.description: Adds tooltip popups to elements with positioning and content.

methods.name: a.fn.popover
methods.description: Provides popover components with title and content sections.

methods.name: a.fn.scrollspy
methods.description: Tracks scroll position and highlights nav items accordingly.

methods.name: a.fn.tab
methods.description: Manages tabbed interfaces for switching views.

methods.name: a.fn.affix
methods.description: Allows an element to become fixed upon scrolling at specified offset.
